ETHICAL USE CLAUSE

SaviorAI is designed to prevent student suicides and reduce mental health
crises. Users of this software agree to:

1. Use the system ONLY for student wellbeing and mental health support
2. NEVER use for surveillance, punishment, or academic performance tracking
3. NEVER sell or monetize student mental health data
4. Obtain explicit informed consent from all monitored students
5. Comply with applicable data protection laws (GDPR, DPDPA, FERPA, etc.)
6. Provide clear opt-out mechanisms for students
7. Ensure human counsellors review all critical interventions
8. Maintain transparency about AI agent decision-making

Violations of these ethical guidelines constitute a breach of the license terms.

